Package org.dcm4che3.audit Description

These are java classes that are created by using XSLT translation on an XML schema that is part of the Dicom standard.

Using versions of the Maven artifact (groupId:javax.xml.bind, artifactId:jaxb-api) with a version less than 2.4 will result in the comments being converted into Javadoc comments incorrectly, with many of the > (greater than) symbols not being converted to the HTML literal &gt. The current version is 2.2.5.

This class is included in the Maven module dcm4che-audit.
